trans-unit.source: Converts a <xref href="System.Drawing.Point"></xref> object from one data type to another.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer en <xref href="System.Drawing.Point"> </xref> objektet fra en datatype til en annen.

trans-unit.source: The PointConverter class is typically used for creating a design-time experience for controls that have properties that are of type <xref:System.Drawing.GraphicsUnit>, and is used to convert points to strings for display in a designer and to convert strings entered in a designer to a <xref:System.Drawing.GraphicsUnit> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PointConverter brukes vanligvis til å opprette en utformingen opplevelse for kolonner som har egenskaper av typen <xref:System.Drawing.GraphicsUnit>, og brukes til å konvertere peker til strenger for visning i en designer og til å konvertere strenger som er angitt i en designer til en <xref:System.Drawing.GraphicsUnit>objektet.</xref:System.Drawing.GraphicsUnit> </xref:System.Drawing.GraphicsUnit>
